<a class="github-fork-ribbon" href="https://github.com/pizidavi/Trakt-Widgets-2" target="_blank" data-ribbon="View on GitHub"></a>

<div class="container my-4">
  <h1>Trakt Widgets<sup style="font-size:60%;">2</sup></h1>
  <p>Trakt Widgets for everyone!</p>

  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <p>Add <em>image</em> in your HTML with url: <a data-append-origin href="/slug/layout/view?language=en">/slug/layout/view?language=en</a></p>

  <h5>Params</h5>
  <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Required</th>
        <th>Default</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>slug</code></td>
        <td><strong>Yes</strong></td>
        <td></td>
        <td>Trakt username (<em>account must be <strong>not private</strong></em>)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>layout</code></td>
        <td><strong>Yes</strong></td>
        <td></td>
        <td>See more in <a href="#layouts">Layouts</a></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>view</code></td>
        <td>No</td>
        <td><code>poster</code></td>
        <td>See more in <a href="#views">Views</a></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h5>Query Param</h5>
  <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Required</th>
        <th>Default</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>language</code></td>
        <td>No</td>
        <td><em>Browser language</em> or <code>en</code></td>
        <td>See more in <a href="#languages">Languages</a></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>
    <em class="me-2">Example:</em>
    <code>&lt;img src="<span data-append-origin></span>/pizidavi/profile/poster" alt="trakt-widget" /&gt;</code>
  </p>

  <h3 id="layouts" class="mt-5">Layouts</h3>
  <p>Possible values: <code>profile</code> - <code>watched</code> - <code>watching</code></p>
  
  <h3 id="views">Views</h3>
  <p>Possible values: <code>poster</code> - <code>card</code> - <code>banner</code> - <code>fanart</code> - <code>fanart-overlay</code> - <code>text</code></p>
  <p><strong>IMPORTANT NOTE:</strong> <code>profile</code> layout works <strong>only</strong> with <code>poster</code> view</p>

